detaileddescription.para:
Generic communication function pointer
dev_id
Place holder to store the id of the device structure Can be used to store the index of the Chip select or I2C address of the device.
reg_addr
Used to select the register the where data needs to be read from or written to.
[in/out]
reg_data: Data array to read/write
len
Length of the data array

period

briefdescription.para: This API is used to set the oversampling, filter and T,P,H, gas selection settings in the sensor.

parameterdescription.para: : Variable used to select the settings which are to be set in the sensor. Macros | Functionality ------------------------------|------------------------------------------- BME680_OST_SEL | To set temperature oversampling. BME680_OSP_SEL | To set pressure oversampling. BME680_OSH_SEL | To set humidity oversampling. BME680_GAS_MEAS_SEL | To set gas measurement setting. BME680_FILTER_SEL | To set filter setting. BME680_HCNTRL_SEL | To set humidity control setting. BME680_RUN_GAS_SEL | To set run gas setting. BME680_NBCONV_SEL | To set NB conversion setting. BME680_GAS_SENSOR_SEL | To set all gas sensor related settings

simplesect.para: : Below are the macros to be used by the user for selecting the desired settings. User can do OR operation of these macros for configuring multiple settings.
